room_title: Escape room "Destiny Origins" by The Escapery in Atlanta
room_address: 1349 Old 41 Hwy NW, Suite 250 Marietta, GA 30060
room_description: You are a team of artifact retrieval experts hired by a swashbuckling archeologist, Dr. Illinois Smith. His arch-rival and nemesis, Dr. Freeman, has a box which contains The Spear of Destiny. The box was stolen by Nazis during WWII from the Vatican. Freeman is working with the KGB to open the box and exploit its power. Your mission is to break into Freeman's office and recover the spear so it may be returned to the Vatican.
